From Candee Ellis Subject Re HELP for Kidney Stones If you think you have kidney stones or your doctor tells you that you do DEFINITELY follow up on My sister was diagnosed with kidney stones years ago and given medication to take to dissolve After that failed and she continued to be in great pain they decided she had When they did exploratory surgery they discovered she had a tumor which turned out to be rhabdomyosarcoma a very rare and agressive I realize this is not what happens in the majority of cases but you never know what can happen and shouldn't take chances